ğŸ’¡ Why It Matters
Protects sensitive data (like PII and financial records)
Prevents accidental deletions or security breaches
Keeps your environment audit-ready and compliant
ğŸ”¥ Pro Tip
Create separate service accounts for each pipeline:
Dataflow SA â†’ limited to job and storage read
BigQuery SA â†’ limited to query or dataset write
Composer SA â†’ limited to orchestration and monitoring
This avoids cross-access and improves traceability.
